<item>If you could ask Joseph Plumb Martin a question, what would you ask, and how do you think he would answer? The passage quoted for this exercise comes from Chapter 3 in Martin’s book. Skim additional chapters of the book to see if you can find clues regarding how he might have responded to your questions.</item>
